{"Sid":0,"Did":126927,"Id":"604565","Title":"員山七賢再興宮手繪彩磁","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collection/63b939ce-1a35-4488-9ae6-5dd205796668/109-her-pa-2513-202011141638205faf66a9552b80.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collection/62e4b7f0-6063-4794-8d46-05009592ea4a/109-her-pa-2513-202011141638205faf66a9552b81.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collection/d8d9e547-a23e-4eae-a0b7-231ca39bd2a0/109-her-pa-2513-202011141638215faf66a9552b82.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collection/5175bbf1-3dca-4f3a-9905-23c98f350c94/109-her-pa-2513-202011141638215faf66a9552b83.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n　　員山七賢再興宮位於員山七賢，背臨蘭陽溪，坐東南朝西北，為單殿式三開間前帶拜亭之廟宇建築。在新建廟宇中，在龍虎兩側的神龕壁面上，均貼飾以宜蘭知名工藝師景陽畫室顏文伯所繪燒之手繪彩磁，包括龍邊神龕的「麒麟送子」，虎邊神龕的「萬事如意」，是較大面積的手繪彩磁。在神龕旁的開門上方，則各有一堵手繪彩磁，龍邊為乘龍吹簫的「蕭史」，一邊為乘鳳吹笙的「弄玉」，一般或稱「乘龍快婿」、「有鳳來儀」，以喻夫妻琴瑟和鳴。\n\n　　在「麒麟送子」手繪彩磁一角有藝師的落款「辛酉年桂月　宜市城隍庙边　景陽　敬画」，辛酉年即1981年；景陽畫室位於宜蘭市城隍街，鄰近宜蘭城隍廟。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY / CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.742887","Keyword_Latitude":"24.718898","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/6B927F92-B6AB-4A06-83A0-DAF5288F22E8","Original_Identifier":"604565","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"景陽畫室 / 萬事如意 / 蕭史弄玉 / 顏文伯 / 麒麟送子","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2021/01/06 18:54:29","timelines":"","place":"","address":"宜蘭縣員山鄉浮洲路11號","longitude":"121.742887","latitude":"24.718898","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"無","writer":"蔡明志/ 林鴻文","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages"